//Upper abdomen

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 09 of Cardio MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
When I select 'Upper abdomen' from the dropdown menu

Then 'Focal liver lesions' checkbox is enabled
And 'Diffuse liver lesion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cholecystolithiasis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Splenomegaly' checkbox is enabled
And 'Hiatal hernia' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mass adrenal gland' checkbox is enabled
And 'Focal lesion of kidney' checkbox is enabled
And 'Urinary retention kidney' checkbox is enabled
And 'Enlarged abd. Lymph nodes' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Focal liver lesions' checkbox
Then 'Benign' radio button is enabled
And 'Malignant' radio button is enabled
And 'Unclear' radio button is enabled
And '> 1 Lesion of the same entity' checkbocx is enabled
When I select 'Benign' radio button
Then 'Cyst' radio button is enabled
And 'Hemangioma' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Diffuse liver lesion' checkbox
Then 'Hemosiderosis' radio button is enabled
And 'Steatosis' radio button is enabled
And 'Cirrhosis' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Mass adrenal gland' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
And 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled


When I select 'Focal lesion of kidney' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
And 'Benign' radio button is enabled
And 'Malignant' radio button is enabled
And 'Unclear' radio button is enabled
And 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled
And '> 1 Lesion of the same entity' checkbocx is enabled
When I select 'Benign' radio button
Then 'Cyst' checkbox is enabled
When I select 'Unclear' radio button
Then 'Complicated cyst' radio button is enabled
And 'Solid mass' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Urinary retention kidney' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
And 'Grade 1' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 2' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 3' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 4' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Enlarged abd. Lymph nodes' checkbox
Then 'Max. diameter, SAD' input field is enabled
And 'Preserved fatty hilum' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspect' radio button is enabled
And 'Confluent' radio button is enabled
